QuestData.Title: Diamondine Sigil of Kazum
QuestData.Description: The sigils of the Abyssal High Council are crafted from the distilled essence of the element of their holder. This sigil was carved from stone, then fused into a faultless diamond.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Diamondine Sigil of Kazum to Warlord Gorchuk in Silithus.
